launched Google Play Services.

00:00:29.060 --> 00:00:30.950
It's an update to Google
Play Services.

00:00:30.950 --> 00:00:33.290
For those of you that aren't
familiar with Google Play

00:00:33.290 --> 00:00:36.910
Services, it is a new platform
through which third-party

00:00:36.910 --> 00:00:40.520
developers, Android developers
can integrate with Google

00:00:40.520 --> 00:00:43.650
services like Google Plus,
OAuth 2.0 authentication.

00:00:43.650 --> 00:00:46.900
