this service is backward

00:00:53.350 --> 00:00:57.270
compatible all the way
back to Froyo or 2.2.

00:00:57.270 --> 00:01:01.620
And the beauty of this is that
for users, as new updates

00:01:01.620 --> 00:01:04.430
become available, the users
automatically get the new

00:01:04.430 --> 00:01:05.800
services on their devices.

00:01:05.800 --> 00:01:10.140
And for developers, all you have
to do is to grab a thin

00:01:10.140 --> 00:01:12.995
client library to integrate
with your Android project.

00:01:16.330 --> 00:01:18.850
MANO MARKS: In this update, we
added a number of interesting

00:01:18.850 --> 00:01:19.680
